== What this is

A Cordova (Phonegap) plugin for the Bump Android API 3.0 (https://github.com/bumptech/bump-api-android). Use Bump (http://bu.mp/) within your Phonegap app to transfer data between clients, based on a physical Bump to pair two devices.

== How to use

* Get a Bump API key.
* Get the Android API into your project: https://github.com/bumptech/bump-api-android.
* Pop the Java and Javascript files into their respective spots in your project (sample folder hierarchy is shown in this repo).
* Go!


